architecture-beta
    group api(cloud)[API tier]
    group data(database)[Data tier]

    service web(server)[Web app] in api
    service api_svc(server)[API service] in api
    service cache(disk)[Cache] in data
    service db(database)[Postgres] in data

    web:R --> L:api_svc
    api_svc:B --> T:db
    api_svc:R --> L:cache
